Body: Date: Tue, 05 Nov 1996 21:00:01 GMT Server: NCSA/1.5 Content-type: text/html Last-modified: Mon, 24 Jun 1996 19:48:18 GMT Content-length: 7090 University of Wisconsin Computer Vision Group The University of Wisconsin - Madison Computer Vision Group is conducting research in designing, implementing and experimenting with important components of computer vision systems.
